fileChanges.details:
Two changes in this file:

1. IMPORT (lines 3-8): Replace SelectControl with ToggleGroupControl and ToggleGroupControlOption in the @wordpress/components import. Change:
  import {
    PanelBody,
    ToggleControl,
    RangeControl,
    SelectControl,
  } from '@wordpress/components';
To:
  import {
    PanelBody,
    ToggleControl,
    RangeControl,
    __experimentalToggleGroupControl as ToggleGroupControl,
    __experimentalToggleGroupControlOption as ToggleGroupControlOption,
  } from '@wordpress/components';

Note: The __experimental prefix with alias is the established convention in this codebase (used in Form.tsx, Accordion.tsx, FullWidthMedia.tsx, ContentWithMedia.tsx, etc.).

2. JSX (lines 112-129): Replace the SelectControl with ToggleGroupControl. Change:
  <SelectControl
    label={ __( 'Pagination mode', 'takt' ) }
    value={ attributes.paginationMode }
    options={ [
      { label: __( 'Load More', 'takt' ), value: 'load-more' },
      { label: __( 'Pagination', 'takt' ), value: 'pagination' },
    ] }
    onChange={ ( value ) => setAttributes( { paginationMode: value } ) }
    __nextHasNoMarginBottom
  />
To:
  <ToggleGroupControl
    label={ __( 'Pagination mode', 'takt' ) }
    value={ attributes.paginationMode }
    onChange={ ( value ) => setAttributes( { paginationMode: value } ) }
    __nextHasNoMarginBottom
    __next40pxDefaultSize
  >
    <ToggleGroupControlOption
      value="load-more"
      label={ __( 'Load More', 'takt' ) }
    />
    <ToggleGroupControlOption
      value="pagination"
      label={ __( 'Pagination', 'takt' ) }
    />
  </ToggleGroupControl>

Note: __next40pxDefaultSize is included to match the convention used by Form.tsx and other blocks in this codebase.
